# Linux Basic Commands & OverTheWire Bandit Practice

## Overview

This lab documents my hands-on practice with Linux command-line fundamentals as part of my cybersecurity learning journey. Rather than focusing only on theory, I practiced each command inside my Kali Linux home lab and reinforced the concepts by solving challenges on OverTheWire Bandit.

The objective of this lab was to become comfortable with Linux navigation, file handling, text processing, and basic command-line operations that are essential for Ethical Hacking, SOC Operations, Penetration Testing, and Cloud Security.

